V0605_01_00_00_0.text:
I've returned to fight!
In the name of the Hanoi!

V0605_01_00_01_0.text: Allow me to erase you from existence.

V0605_01_00_02_0.text: This Duel is the beginning of your end!

V0605_01_00_03_0.text: Since you're a worthy competitor, I'm going to enjoy this.

V0605_01_00_05_0.text: I don't care who you are.

V0605_01_00_05_1.text:
There are plenty who despise me.
You're nothing special.

V0605_01_00_06_0.text: I'm going to enjoy this Duel, Playmaker!

V0605_01_00_07_0.text:
Soulburner...
If you want a fight, you got one.

V0605_01_00_08_0.text:
I respect you, Gore.
That's why I'm going to crush you.

V0605_01_00_10_0.text: If it isn't The Shepherd - lone wolf of the wasteland.

V0605_01_00_11_0.text: I'll do what my father couldn't - eliminate you!

V0605_01_00_12_0.text: It's my personal mission to delete every Ignis!

V0605_01_00_13_0.text: My Dueling is far greater than you can ever imagine!

V0605_01_00_14_0.text: Ignis, you should feel proud that I'm the one to erase you!

V0605_01_00_15_0.text: The future you desire will lead to nothing!

V0605_03_00_01_0.text: If you won't give up, I have no choice but to make you!

V0605_03_00_04_0.text: You failed to eliminate all my LP.

V0605_03_00_05_0.text: You should never feel too comfortable during a Duel.

V0605_05_00_00_0.text:
I won't run from my destiny!
I will conquer this moment!

V0605_06_01_03_0.text: You think I'll let you do that?

V0605_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0605_07_09_01_0.text: I'll use the card I Set!

V0605_11_01_00_0.text: I Summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0605_11_10_02_1.text:
I set my monsters in the Link Arrows!
Link the circuit!

V0605_14_00_01_0.text: With this battle, there's no coming back for you!

V0605_16_00_01_0.text: What a sad way for you to end.

V0605_21_00_00_0.text:
You're tougher than I thought.
But you'll still lose.

V0605_21_00_01_0.text:
Congrats on surviving.
But you won't for long!

V0605_21_00_02_0.text: With this, I end my turn.

V0605_21_00_04_0.text:
You've been stopping my moves.
But can you keep that up?

V0605_21_00_05_0.text: Even if I'm down to 1 LP, I'm still favored to win.

V0605_28_00_00_0.text:
The winner wins all.
The loser loses all.
That's Dueling.

V0605_28_00_01_0.text: I'm not one to fall for your foolish strategies.

V0605_28_00_02_0.text: I won't run from what needs to be done!

V0605_28_00_03_0.text:
I have a mission.
And I won't stop until I complete it!

V0605_28_00_05_0.text: Memories of my father are what push me to succeed!

V0605_28_00_06_0.text: Playmaker, you're incapable of outwitting me.

V0605_28_00_07_0.text:
Instead of whining, try Dueling.
Or you'll never defeat me!

V0605_28_00_08_0.text:
I like your spirit.
But spirit doesn't win Duels.

V0605_28_00_09_0.text:
You Duel as well as you hunt.
Meaning not good at all.

V0605_28_00_10_0.text: I will finish what my father started, Ignis!

V0605_28_00_11_0.text: I knew the Ignis were nothing but a glitch in the system!

V0605_28_00_12_0.text: Your arrogance is your downfall, Ignis!

V0605_28_00_13_0.text: Ignis, you've been evil since the day you were created.

V0605_28_00_13_1.text: You're a programming glitch that doesn't deserve to exist!

V0605_29_00_00_0.text: It didn't go my way today...

V0605_29_00_01_0.text:
This Duel is only the beginning.
I will be back!

V0605_29_00_02_0.text: My father taught me that success comes from failure.

V0605_29_00_04_0.text: Just remember - I won't run from my destiny!

V0605_29_00_05_0.text: This is why you're my most formidable foe, Playmaker.

V0605_29_00_08_0.text: The Shepherd has too much pride to lose...

V0605_29_00_09_0.text:
Argh...
Since when were the Ignis so unpredictable?

V0605_33_00_01_0.text: Witness a Duel that transcends the limits of the mind!

V0605_33_00_02_0.text: I will crush you until you no longer exist!

V0605_33_00_03_0.text:
These winds rage for me...
And me alone!

V0605_33_00_03_1.text:
I activate my Skill to get what I want!
Storm Access!

V0605_33_00_04_0.text:
I activate my Skill!
The fiercest is within my grasp!

V0605_33_00_05_0.text:
I activate my Skill!
Bring me power!

V0605_33_00_05_2.text: The Stardust Road is my path to victory.

V0605_30_00_01_0.text: I'm not as kind as you think.

V0605_30_00_02_0.text: Nothing in the digital world is real!

V0605_34_00_00_0.text: The digital world must not affect the real world!

V0605_34_00_01_0.text: Take your pick: Lose quickly or lose painfully?

V0605_34_00_02_0.text: I don't need to apologize for anything I've done!

V0605_34_00_03_0.text: I never understand the strategies of the weak.

V0605_34_00_04_0.text: You'll be an excellent guinea pig to test my deck.

V0605_34_00_05_0.text: Your deck seems to finally be working.

V0605_34_00_06_0.text: When I win, I win with style.

V0605_34_00_07_0.text: You don't have the spine to be a Duelist!

V0605_34_00_10_0.text: Allow me to give you three reasons why you will not survive!

V0605_34_00_11_0.text: One: I hold the advantage in LP, monsters and cards.

V0605_34_00_12_0.text: Two: My desire to win is greater than yours.

V0605_34_00_13_0.text: And three: I’m just a better Duelist than you.

V0605_32_00_01_0.text:
Yu-Gi-Oh! Duel Links!
Link into the VRAINS!

V0605_35_00_00_0.text: I've returned to face my destiny.

V0605_35_00_01_0.text: I Duel for the Knights of Hanoi!

V0605_36_00_03_0.text:
I leave this to you, Playmaker.
...And Ai.

V0605_08_00_34_0.text: Fall before the might of the Hanoi!
